### Miles Room Booking API - HTTP Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token =

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### Authentication
### ============================================

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@miles.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@miles.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### Locations
### ============================================

### Get all locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/locations

### Get specific location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/locations/stavanger

### Create location (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Austin Office",
  "address": "123 Congress Ave",
  "city": "Austin",
  "country": "USA",
  "timezone": "America/Chicago",
  "description": "New Texas office"
}

### Update location
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/locations/stavanger
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated headquarters in San Francisco"
}

### ============================================
### Rooms
### ============================================

### Get all rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms

### Get rooms by location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms?locationId=stavanger

### Get specific room
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/stavanger-skagen

### Check room availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/stavanger-skagen/availability?startDate=2025-10-20T00:00:00Z&endDate=2025-10-21T00:00:00Z

### Create room
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "MÃ¸terom 1",
  "locationId": "stavanger",
  "capacity": 8,
  "amenities": ["whiteboard", "video_conference", "tv"],
  "description": "Meeting room 1"
}

### Update room
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/rooms/stavanger-skagen
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "capacity": 12
}

### ============================================
### Bookings
### ============================================

### Get all bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get bookings by room
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?roomId=stavanger-skagen
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get bookings by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?startDate=2025-10-20T00:00:00Z&endDate=2025-10-27T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "stavanger-skagen",
  "startTime": "2025-10-22T14:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-10-22T15:30:00Z",
  "title": "Product Review Meeting",
  "description": "Monthly product review"
}

### Update booking
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/BOOKING_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Meeting Title",
  "startTime": "2025-10-22T15:00:00Z"
}

### Cancel booking
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/BOOKING_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### Calendar Feeds
### ============================================

### Get office calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calendar/office/stavanger.ics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get room calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calendar/room/stavanger-skagen.ics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user calendar
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/calendar/user/USER_ID.ics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
